%% Level 2 — login and register (discovery stub)

sequenceDiagram
  actor User as Partner user
  participant App as Partner portal
  participant IdP as Identity provider

  alt Register
    User->>App: Submit org email and metadata
    App->>IdP: Sign-up flow
    IdP-->>App: Account created
    App-->>User: Success
  else Login
    User->>App: Credentials / SSO
    App->>IdP: Authenticate
    IdP-->>App: Tokens / session
    App-->>User: Access to configuration
  end
